This folder contains example files to run various inflow perturbation methods.

WRF_CPM:

This folder contains files to execute

     1. Idealized WRF two-domain, one-way nested simulations using
        the cell perturbation method on the nested LES domain,

     2. Periodic single-domain LES to generate data to force and
     	evaluate the nested LES results from the two-domain setup.

